<node id="The Creative Habit">
  <data key="d0">The Creative Habit</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Creative Habit is a work that provides various exercises and techniques to enhance creative thinking and problem-solving.&lt;SEP&gt;The Creative Habit is a book that provides various creative exercises and techniques to overcome blocks and enhance creativity.&lt;SEP&gt;The Creative Habit is a framework that discusses the importance of self-reliance and individual responsibility in collaborative processes.&lt;SEP&gt;The Creative Habit is a book by Twyla Tharp that provides insights and exercises for developing creative habits and overcoming blocks.&lt;SEP&gt;The Creative Habit is a book that provides insights and exercises to develop creative habits and overcome mental barriers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d7fecbb0e15b0c2fecb3e2017d03f5ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9eb663934a3ed47aa6b9e9a91e67a150&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbdaf67f545ba6445a0c79806926980f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d6577a0585d9b51783360fe50194d32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a970b600a07208f04d90f0b45eea4de</data>
