  <data key="d5">1774652538</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Steps">
  <data key="d0">Steps</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Steps outline a process for managing fear in creative work by acknowledging its presence and setting boundaries.&lt;SEP&gt;Steps outlines the sequential actions or procedures to follow in executing a particular creative method.&lt;SEP&gt;Steps outline the specific actions to be taken for each exercise in The Creative Habit, guiding users through the creative process.&lt;SEP&gt;Steps outline a series of actions to perform for creative exercises aimed at enhancing productivity and overcoming mental blocks.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d7fecbb0e15b0c2fecb3e2017d03f5ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5bfa64481a8d63180f365f8cb3d39ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbdaf67f545ba6445a0c79806926980f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-324826e69646e9a60494746cffe0957b</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774652539</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Template">
  <data key="d0">Template</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Template provides a structured format for expressing the relationship between creativity and the presence of fear.&lt;SEP&gt;Template is a predefined structure that guides the documentation of the outcomes of each creative method.&lt;SEP&gt;Template is a structured format provided in The Creative Habit to help users organize their ideas or responses effectively.&lt;SEP&gt;Template provides standardized phrases or structures to guide participants in their writing or creative processes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d7fecbb0e15b0c2fecb3e2017d03f5ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5bfa64481a8d63180f365f8cb3d39ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbdaf67f545ba6445a0c79806926980f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-324826e69646e9a60494746cffe0957b</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774652539</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Failure-Mode Fix">
  <data key="d0">Failure-Mode Fix</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Failure-Mode Fix refers to strategies intended to address potential challenges or obstacles that may arise during the application of creative methods.&lt;SEP&gt;Failure-Mode Fix provides strategies for managing overwhelming fear during creative processes by changing physical locations.&lt;SEP&gt;Failure-Mode Fix refers to strategies provided in various exercises to overcome potential pitfalls during creative tasks.&lt;SEP&gt;Failure-Mode Fix suggests alternative strategies to address challenges that may arise during the creative exercises in The Creative Habit.&lt;SEP&gt;The Failure-Mode Fix provides strategies for overcoming obstacles when one cannot leave their workspace, encouraging tidiness and posture adjustment.&lt;SEP&gt;Failure-Mode Fix is a strategy to simplify complicated explanations or processes by using basic language or visual aids.&lt;SEP&gt;Failure-mode fix suggests alternative strategies to employ when participants encounter resistance or obstacles during creative tasks.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d7fecbb0e15b0c2fecb3e2017d03f5ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5bfa64481a8d63180f365f8cb3d39ee&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9eb663934a3ed47aa6b9e9a91e67a150&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cbdaf67f545ba6445a0c79806926980f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-324826e69646e9a60494746cffe0957b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8160382cd709adb42688285242ef8fab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d6577a0585d9b51783360fe50194d32</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
