  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">20-Minute Image Tear is an activity aimed at generating visual inspiration by cutting and arranging images from magazines.&lt;SEP&gt;The 20-Minute Image Tear is a creativity method involving tearing images from magazines for visual inspiration in a project.</data>
